high_descs: Make a right to walk to the glass table.
Pick up the keys on the glass table.
Turn around to hang a right towards the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at some keys by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk slightly forward and turn left towards the dining table.
Pick up the key chain from the dining table.
Turn around, walk forward to the wall, then turn right and walk to the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a key chain by the dim natural light of a living room.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward a step, turn left, go forward to the table.
Take the keys from the table.
Turn around, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the lamp.
Turn the switch of the lamp so it is off.
anns.task_desc: Bring keys to a lamp that is not lit.
